\cf0 \ul \ulc0 Note that the builds that I provide use Universal binaries\ulnone  of Allegro and enet. \
For Allegro, I set the 
\f1 CFLAGS
\f0  and 
\f1 LDFLAGS
\f0  environment variables to 
\f1 -arch i386 -arch ppc
\f0  before running ./configure.\
For enet, I had a bit more difficulty and had to individually compile separate libraries with the two different architectures, then merge the two into one using the 
\f1 lipo
\f0  tool.\
